### RESQID — Token Inventory API Tests
### File: src/request/tokens.http
### =============================================================================

@baseUrl  = http://localhost:3000/api/school-admin
@token    = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..HEXYWKielRn9_cqagsYcStwPdxz1WgNLLO9NpbiWbwU
@schoolId = ee20bd32-c539-4489-ae22-ce35c4b24a7b
@badUUID  = ee20bd32-c539-4489-ae22-ce35c4b24a8b

### =============================================================================
### ✅ HAPPY PATH
### =============================================================================

### [1] All tokens — page 1, limit 12 (default)
### Response includes: tokens[], stats{}, meta{}
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/tokens
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [2] Filter ACTIVE only
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/tokens?status=ACTIVE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [3] Filter UNASSIGNED — no student linked
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/tokens?status=UNASSIGNED
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [4] Filter EXPIRED
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/tokens?status=EXPIRED
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [5] Filter REVOKED
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/tokens?status=REVOKED
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [6] Search by token hash prefix
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/tokens?search=a3f
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [7] Search by student name
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/tokens?search=aarav
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [8] Status filter + search combined
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/tokens?status=ACTIVE&search=sharma
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [9] Page 2, limit 12
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/tokens?page=2&limit=12
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [10] Large page size (max 100)
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/tokens?limit=100
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [11] Second request — stats should be Redis cached (check logs: no groupBy query)
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/tokens
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### =============================================================================
### ❌ VALIDATION ERRORS — rejected at middleware, never hits DB
### =============================================================================

### [12] No auth — expect 401
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/tokens
Accept: application/json

###

### [13] Invalid schoolId — expect 400 VALIDATION_ERROR
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{badUUID}}/tokens
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [14] Wrong school (tenant mismatch) — expect 403 FORBIDDEN
GET {{baseUrl}}/00000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000000/tokens
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [15] Invalid status value — expect 400 VALIDATION_ERROR
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/tokens?status=INVALID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [16] limit over 100 — expect 400 VALIDATION_ERROR
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{schoolId}}/tokens?limit=500
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###
